<plot>Come as You Are is a stylised and colourful exploration of three individuals who have created an alter ego which offers an outlet from their normal daily lives. Each is a separate journey into the terrain of sexuality, identity and fantasy within the urban landscape. A drag queen, a sexual outlaw and an urban cowboy reveal what lies behind the 'mask'.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?111610</url></doc>
